#include <bits/stdc++.h>
 
using namespace std;
 
#define MAX 1123456
typedef long long ll;
 
ll a[MAX];
 
int main() {
 
	int t; scanf("%d", &t);
 
	while(t--) {
 
		int N, M; scanf("%d %d", &N, &M);
 
		for(int i = 0; i < N; i++) scanf("%d", &a[i]);
 
		ll sum = 0;
		int i = 0;
 
		for(; i < M; i++) sum += a[i];
 
		for(;  i < N; i++)
			sum -= (ll)(ceil(a[i]/2));
 
		if(sum < 0)
			cout << "DEFEAT" << endl;
		else
			cout << "VICTORY" << endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
